channel.title: Hamachi
channel.description: Ok, I got hamachi downloaded, got the name of the server in and password and I get a screen that lists a bunch of names and ips. How do I get to the server from this?

If you wanna join, just click join network and put the username and pass then your in the network then find what the port is and the IP and you should be able to logg in. If not, server’s proberly down.

item.dc:creator: @warmwaddle warmwaddle
item.description:
@warmwaddle wrote:

The many IPs are other people who joined the network. Now that you have joined it, it gives you the ability to use the owner’s ip and log onto his server. So now just try logging on.
